OL,7,FThe UK could see a repeat of last
OL,8,Fsummer's riots as lessons have not
OL,9,Fbeen learned from the unrest, a former
OL,10,Fgovernment advisor has warned.
OL,12,FDame Sara Khan said that she 'wasn't
OL,13,Fwholly surprised' when the unrest
OL,14,Fbroke out in towns and cities across
OL,15,Fthe UK last year, claiming the
OL,16,F'warning signs were flashing red'.
OL,18,FBut, the government's former counter
OL,19,Fextremist commissioner, admitted the
OL,20,Fseverity and scale of the disorder was
OL,21,F'without a doubt, shocking'.
