OL,3,C'Repeat of last year's riots
OL,4,Cinevitable as government has failed to
OL,5,Cact'
OL,7,FDame Sara, who was previously tasked
OL,8,Fwith overseeing a review into social
OL,9,Fcohesion for the government, went on
OL,10,Fto claim she 'didn't doubt' the UK
OL,11,Fcould see more unrest this summer.
OL,13,FDame Sara spoke to ITV News West
OL,14,FCountry as part of an investigation
OL,15,Finto the long term impact of the 2024
OL,16,Friots in the South West.
OL,18,FTalking to ITV West Country, she said
OL,19,F'worst case scenario' would be: "That
OL,20,Fwe see a recurrence of what happened
OL,21,Fin the summer.
