OL,3,C'Repeat of last year's riots
OL,4,Cinevitable as government has failed to
OL,5,Cact'
OL,7,F"I worry that in the time frame
OL,8,Fbetween the two summers, that lessons
OL,9,Fhave not been learned, that the
OL,10,Fgovernment has not put in a strategic
OL,11,Fapproach to prevent and deal with this.
OL,13,F"I mean I think it's a really good
OL,14,Ftime to ask the government: what have
OL,15,Fyou been doing post Southport? What
OL,16,Fare you putting in place to make sure
OL,17,Fthat we don't see a repeat of what we
OL,18,Fsaw last summer?
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
