OL,7,F"I knew from last year that there was
OL,8,Fnothing in place, has anything changed
OL,9,Fsince that time?
OL,11,F"Because, if it hasn't, that's a
OL,12,Freally concerning question for
OL,13,Fgovernment and for government
OL,14,Fdepartments."
OL,16,FDame Sara, who was the government's
OL,17,Fcounter extremism commissioner between
OL,18,F2018 and 2021, previously did a review
OL,19,Finto social cohesion for the
OL,20,Fgovernment.
