OL,7,FIn her March 2024 report she warned
OL,8,Fthe 'Whitehall machinery' was not
OL,9,Fequipped to deal with growing threats
OL,10,Fto social cohesion.
OL,12,FShe explained extremists exploiting
OL,13,Flocal tensions, disinformation
OL,14,Fspreading via social media, increasing
OL,15,Fdeprivation during the cost of living
OL,16,Fcrisis, a breaking down of social
OL,17,Fcohesion and increasing distrust in
OL,18,Fauthorities - was "feeding anger and
OL,19,Ffuelling division".
