OL,7,FAsked why we hadn't seen the riots
OL,8,Fcoming, she said: "Well of course, I
OL,9,Fthink some of us did see it coming.
OL,11,F"I think the question is whether the
OL,12,Fgovernment saw it coming and they
OL,13,Fshould have seen it coming because the
OL,14,Fwriting was on the wall for a number
OL,15,Fof years.
