OL,3,C'Repeat of last year's riots
OL,4,Cinevitable as government has failed to
OL,5,Cact'
OL,7,F"The signs were flashing red - let's
OL,8,Fbe very clear about that - and the
OL,9,Ftension was building that the
OL,10,Fdiscourse in public I think around
OL,11,Fimmigration, becoming increasingly
OL,12,Fmore toxic as well.
OL,14,F"Now the question is - why hadn't the
OL,15,Fgovernment or even local authorities
OL,16,Fdone more to tackle this. Because,
OL,17,Flike I said, the warning signs were,
OL,18,Fwithout a doubt, flashing red."
