OL,3,C'Repeat of last year's riots
OL,4,Cinevitable as government has failed to
OL,5,Cact'
OL,7,FShe added: "While the police were
OL,8,Fexcellent in dealing with the summer
OL,9,Friots under very difficult
OL,10,Fcircumstances, we have to remember and
OL,11,Fappreciate that's a downstream
OL,12,Fapproach.
OL,14,F"But, where is the upstream approach
OL,15,Fto prevent, to identify, prevent and
OL,16,Frespond to tensions when they are
OL,17,Fbreaking out, or to address the
OL,18,Fgrievances that people have.
OL,26,@oD@LOUvD@AOU
