OL,3,C'Repeat of last year's riots
OL,4,Cinevitable as government has failed to
OL,5,Cact'
OL,7,F"That just doesn't exist and that's
OL,8,Fwhy many local authorities, when I
OL,9,Fspoke to them, said they were
OL,10,Fstruggling because there is no central
OL,11,Fgovernment guidance or strategy to
OL,12,Fprevent such activity."
OL,14,FDespite the bleak warnings, Dame Sara
OL,15,Fsaid it was important not to lose hope
OL,16,Fand praised the 'British bulldog
OL,17,Fspirit' which saw 'anti-racist
OL,18,Fprotesters coming out, reclaiming the
OL,19,Fstreets' during the unrest.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
