OL,7,FShe added: "We know the vast majority
OL,8,Fof people did not support those
OL,9,Fviolent protesters - that they did not
OL,10,Fsupport the rioters and I think we
OL,11,Fneed to galvanize and mobilise that
OL,12,Fsentiment.
OL,14,F"I live in hope, I really do and I
OL,15,Fthink that's because we live in a
OL,16,Ffantastic country of people who really
OL,17,Fcare about living in a socially
OL,18,Fcohesive society.
OL,26,@oD@LOUvD@AOU
