OL,7,F"But at the same time I think we have
OL,8,Fto recognise there are serious
OL,9,Fchallenges, there are serious threats
OL,10,Ffacing us, and we all, as a society
OL,11,Fcollectively, have to play our part."
OL,13,FA government spokesperson said: "The
OL,14,Fviolence that spilled out onto our
OL,15,Fstreets last year was inexcusable and
OL,16,Fcommunities are still feeling the
OL,17,Fimpact now.
