OL,7,F"We've seen years of decline and
OL,8,Funderinvestment in our communities,
OL,9,Fpublic services decimated, and
OL,10,Fgovernments who have eroded the trust
OL,11,Fof the British people they were
OL,12,Felected to serve.
OL,14,F"That's why we're working hard across
OL,15,Fgovernment to provide support for our
OL,16,Fcommunities through our Plan for
OL,17,FChange and tackle issues that have
OL,18,Fbeen ignored for too long, in the
OL,19,Fpursuit of national renewal.
